name: Amanogawa
skill: Deals 3728/4568 DMG to the enemy with the most HP.
ability: Sharply increases Skill DMG and Crit DMG.

additional_data.description: The spirit of the stars that light up the night sky. She lives somewhere between Orihime and Hikoboshi in order to better observe them. She used to love keeping an eye on them, but now she's just going through the motions. They seem to be falling into a regular day-to-day pattern...and growing a little complacent? Or maybe everything is going perfectly? In any case, she claims to be bored now that the bittersweetness is gone from the pair's interactions. Who knows how she really feels deep down inside, though...
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Limited Jewel Summon 14/06/17- 05/07/17
◦ Trade at Exchange for 50 Mochi 02/07/17 - 05/07/17
additional_data.notes_and_trivia:
◦ Double Wish Tablet drops by 33% during the "Coastal Calamity - Tanabata Beach Contest" event.
◦ The effect increases with the number of limit breaks. (33% → 49.75% → 66.5% → 83.25% → 100%)
◦ Summon rate increased until 17/05/17- 07/06/17
◦ She is also referred to as Milkana Wayford

summon: "You know what they say, all roads lead to ROMANCE!"
